    @{" RecordMacro     " LINK "RecordMacro" 0} - Start recording a macro
    @{" SaveMacro       " LINK "SaveMacro" 0} - Save the currently recorded macro

  Commands dealing with external Tools or ARexx macros

    @{" ExecARexxMacro  " LINK "ExecARexxMacro" 0} - Execute am ARexx script
    @{" ExecARexxString " LINK "ExecARexxString" 0} - Execute an ARexx string
    @{" ExecDosScript   " LINK "ExecDosScript" 0} - Execute a DOS script
    @{" ExecTool        " LINK "ExecTool" 0} - Execute syncronously a Tool
    @{" NewShell        " LINK "NewShell" 0} - Opens a new shell
    @{" RunTool         " LINK "RunTool" 0} - Run asynchronously the selected Tool

  Commands dealing with the configuration of the program

    @{" GetPrefs        " LINK "GetPrefs" 0} - Return the value of the specified preference
    @{" OpenDefinitions " LINK "OpenDefinitions" 0} - Load the specified definitions file for the current document
    @{" OpenPrefs       " LINK "OpenPrefs" 0} - Load the specified preference file for the current document
    @{" SaveDefPrefs    " LINK "SaveDefPrefs" 0} - Save the preferences on disk, as defaults
    @{" SavePrefs       " LINK "SavePrefs" 0} - Save the preferences on disk
    @{" SetPrefs        " LINK "SetPrefs" 0} - Set the specified preference

  Commands dealing with windows ands screen

    @{" ActivateLastDoc " LINK "ActivateLastDoc" 0} - Activates and bring to front the last document
    @{" ActivateNextDoc " LINK "ActivateNextDoc" 0} - Activates and bring to front the next document
    @{" ActivatePrevDoc " LINK "ActivatePrevDoc" 0} - Activates and grong to front the previous document
