@NODE "Errors_Reference" "Errors Reference"

  @{title "Errors Reference"}

  This is the reference for error codes and messages.

  The first list contains the errors caused during the normal use of
  the program, the second and the third contain errors occurred while
  parsing, respectively, definitions and preferences files.

    @{" Blacks Editor errors " LINK "Errors_Bed" 0}

    @{" Definitions file errors " LINK "Errors_Defs" 0}

    @{" Preferences file errors " LINK "Errors_Prefs" 0}

@ENDNODE

